data.description: Discover comfortable living in this stunning ranch-style home! Has three bedrooms strategically laid out, ensuring privacy for the Primary suite. Primary bedroom offers a custom tile shower and a spacious Walk-in Closet. Captivating great room with vaulted ceilings, open concept kitchen surrounded by custom cabinets, convenient pantry, breakfast bar, and dining area. Living room exudes warmth, the gas fireplace complements the custom Amish mantle. The lower level unveils a finished office/craft room, setting the stage for potential family/rec. room, 4th bedroom, and future full bath. Enjoy the convenience of a generous 3+ car garage, a back deck, and a patio for outdoor relaxation. New furnace and roof installed in 2023.
